data.description: Don't miss out on this spacious 2-story home with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths located in Hunters Chase. Easy access to I-10. Downstairs features a wonderful primary suite, living room, formal dining, remodeled kitchen with breakfast area, utliity room, and a half bath. Upstairs features 3 large bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a massive gameroom. Home is situated on a culdesac street. Washer & Dryer included. What are you waiting for? Come view the home today!
